headline: KeyBanc changes rating, PT on industrials following a mixed Q3
summary: Investing.com - KeyBanc Capital Markets on Friday revised ratings and price target on industrial sector stocks following a mixed third quarter earnings, as companies navigate macroeconomic conditions, with management flagging about visibility into 2025.
